ZH: 我每天早上都喜欢花时间梳妆。
EN: I like to spend time dressing up every morning.

ZH: 她在镜子前梳妆的时候总是很仔细。
EN: She is always very meticulous when she dresses up in front of the mirror.

ZH: 妈妈告诉我要记住每天梳妆打扮。
EN: Mom told me to remember to dress up every day.

ZH: 梳妆台上摆放着她的化妆品。
EN: Her cosmetics are placed on the dressing table.

ZH: 他们在某个晚上一起梳妆打扮，为了一场特殊的活动。
EN: They dressed up together one evening for a special event.

ZH: 姐姐被我从她的梳妆台上吓了一跳。
EN: My sister got startled when I surprised her at her dressing table.

ZH: 每次她梳妆的时候，总是能看到她的微笑。
EN: Every time she dresses up, you can always see her smile.

ZH: 她感觉自信，因为她刚刚梳妆完成。
EN: She feels confident after just finishing dressing up.

ZH: 这个新梳妆镜可以放大五倍。
EN: This new dressing mirror can zoom in up to five times.

ZH: 她在梳妆台上整理她的头发。
EN: She is styling her hair at the dressing table.

ZH: 她用那把梳子梳妆打扮头发。
EN: She styles her hair with that comb.

ZH: 妹妹正在梳妆台前试穿不同的服装。
EN: My younger sister is trying on different outfits in front of the dressing table.

ZH: 她梳妆的时候通常会戴着耳环。
EN: She usually wears earrings when she dresses up.

ZH: 我上个月给梳妆镜换了灯泡。
EN: I changed the light bulb for the dressing mirror last month.

ZH: 他在我的梳妆台上撒了一些灰尘。
EN: He sprinkled some dust on my dressing table.

ZH: 她正在梳妆，不想被打扰。
EN: She is dressing up and doesn't want to be disturbed.

ZH: 妈妈教会我如何正确地梳妆。
EN: Mom taught me how to dress up properly.

ZH: 去参加晚宴之前，我一定要好好梳妆打扮。
EN: I must dress up nicely before attending the dinner party.

ZH: 她的梳妆台收纳了各种不同的化妆品。
EN: Her dressing table accommodates various types of cosmetics.

ZH: 请你帮我拿一下梳妆台上的镜子。
EN: Could you please help me bring the mirror on the dressing table?

ZH: 她那张梳妆台很漂亮，上面有许多蔷薇花的图案。
EN: Her dressing table is beautiful, with a rose pattern on it.
